race.comment: NIGEL DEVERE (1) finished a 4.5 lengths second last start over 515m at Sandown in a quick 29.47. Expected to push the clock again here. JUNGLE JOHNNY (2) impressed on both occasions winning in best times, 34.19 latest and 29.29 two back. In great form and can continue his winning ways. VINCENT BALE (7) boasts a strong record this course with four wins and four minors from nine tries. Scored by 0.8 lengths last time (27.78) in a Grade 4/5 over 485m at Horsham. Looks one of the chances. ZIG ZAG MAN (6) won with authority last start. Sure to run well again.

runners.name: Nigel Devere
